 <PERSON> Jonathan </PERSON> <PERSON> Wolman </PERSON> is assistant bureau chief for the <ORGANIZATION> Associated </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Press </ORGANIZATION> in <LOCATION> Washington </LOCATION>.
