dued him and took him behind his truck, where he was shot. <PERSON> Walz </PERSON> said <PERSON> Bedoni </PERSON> was seen after that shooting with a gun hin his hand, and was seen pointing a gun at <PERSON> Begay </PERSON>, who had been summoned to the scene. All four defense attorneys maintained their clients were not at the crime scene, and said prosecution witnesses' reliability would be an issue. The trial is being held in federal court because the killing occurred on an Indian reservation.
