ssed <LOCATION> U.S. </LOCATION> principle of non-intervention in our internal affairs,'' <PERSON> Urgban </PERSON> said. As for Solidarity, he said: `` Whoever receives a soldier's pay from an alien power can neither define itself as an independent force nor a Polish force.''
