 The <ORGANIZATION> Salvation </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Army </ORGANIZATION> has honored President <PERSON> Reagan </PERSON> for his leadership in encouraging voluntary, private efforts to help the needy. At a White House cerermony, he was presented with the <ORGANIZATION> Army </ORGANIZATION>'s `` Others Award,'' saying his `` leadership has encouraged voluntarism and private sector initiative to the benefit of others in all parts of our society.
